@startuml
state "Waiting for Customer Choice" as WaitingForChoice
state ProcessingWithdrawal
state ProcessingCustomWithdrawal
state Ejecting

[*] --> WaitingForChoice

WaitingForChoice --> ProcessingWithdrawal : Withdrawal Selected / Request Withdrawal
WaitingForChoice --> ProcessingCustomWithdrawal : Custom Amount Entered / Enter Custom Amount
WaitingForChoice --> Ejecting : Cancel / Eject

ProcessingWithdrawal --> Ejecting : Rejected / Eject
ProcessingCustomWithdrawal --> Ejecting : Rejected / Eject

Ejecting --> ProcessingWithdrawal : Continue Withdrawal / Continue Transaction
Ejecting --> ProcessingCustomWithdrawal : Continue Custom / Continue Transaction
Ejecting --> [*] : End Transaction
@enduml
